# AskQuestion Notch Notification

Before every AskQuestion call, run a Shell command to notify the MacBook notch
(Open Island). This lets the user see the question in the notch and click to
jump back to Cursor when they are in another app.

## Rule

Immediately before calling AskQuestion, call Shell (with `block_until_ms: 3000`) to run:

```
python3 ~/.cursor/scripts/cursor-askquestion-notifier.py "CONVERSATION_ID" "QUESTION_TITLE"
```

- `CONVERSATION_ID`: the current conversation/session UUID
- `QUESTION_TITLE`: the `title` field you are about to pass to AskQuestion

Run this Shell call in parallel with the AskQuestion call (same tool-call batch).
